# üìò STUDY. REIMAGINED.
## Redefine what's possible.

### INTRODUCING. The Ultimate Digital Notebook. Created for You.

Your study notes should be free.
There is no longer any need to waste time on Word's clumsy layouts or endless formatting corrections.

**We created an environment where your focus belongs solely to your learning.**
This is Quarto, powered by the RStudio Visual Editor.

---
## 1. SIMPLICITY. Transfer your thoughts, instantly.

Your ideas and knowledge should not be hindered by buttons and settings.

* **It features View Mode.** Edit directly on the screen, just like writing on paper. Cluttered ribbon menus are obsolete.
* **Master only 3 actions.** Define a heading, bold key phrases, and organize with lists. These are the only actions essential for your learning.
* **Layouts complete themselves.** No need to adjust pages or margins. The moment you write it, it becomes a perfected study asset.

---
## 2. PURE INTEGRATION. Integrate AI intelligence in an instant.

Seamlessly incorporate insights gained from conversation. This is the new way to learn.

* **AI Summaries. Perfected.** Complex formatting generated by AI is instantly unified to your notebook's style the moment you paste it.
* **Correction is a relic of the past.** You are spared the effort. We protect your time and energy.

---
## 3. UNBREAKABLE. Data That Endures. Guaranteed Peace of Mind.

Your learning journey will never be lost. This system prioritizes your data protection.

### You only need to remember two rules.

#### **RULE 1. [RECORD]**

> # ‚ÄúWhen in doubt, commit. GitHub takes it from there.‚Äù

* **Never fear overwriting.** Your data is safe, even if you make a mistake. GitHub records all history, allowing for instant restoration.

#### **RULE 2. [OUTPUT]**

> # ‚ÄúWhen in doubt, sync. Python takes it from there.‚Äù

* **The final form is automatic.** Once you complete the sync on your Mac, our system will automatically generate all your notes as beautiful, unified PDFs or web pages.
* **Your job is simply to write.**

---
## FINALLY. This is what you need to learn.

There is no longer any need to learn the complexities of Word.
You only need to focus on **‚Äúwhat to write.‚Äù**

**Open RStudio. Switch to View Mode. Start writing.**
Your learning begins now.